title: 'Star Trek' warps into 2026 with epic 'Space For Everybody' Rose Parade float
description: 2026 is a special year for creator Gene Roddenberry's iconic "Wagon Train To The Stars" sci-fi franchise as it celebrates its 60th anniversary seeking out new life and new civilizations!
